{"tid":2234992,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"護士其實係咪長期精神失常？","createTime":"2020-10-08T10:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T11:57:31.000Z","uid":42402,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"39dc65f50fbde6fb3f789880f2c021c8864fa9b9","tid":2234992,"uid":42402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"呂護士：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呂護士：你可以返去先 手術後再返<br />\n我：唔洗 我喺到坐陣先<br />\n呂護士：有排做㗎 你走先啦<br />\n我：我坐一陣先<br />\n呂護士：唉 唔理你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後晏就<br />\n<br />\n我企喺到等冧巴<br />\n<br />\n呂護士：我坐係到等啦<br />\n我：唔洗 我企喺到得啦<br />\n呂護士：你唔好企喺到啦<br />\n我：我企喺角落頭 唔阻你<br />\n呂護士：唉 你鍾意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問佢係咪當咗我係佢條仔 要俾佢管？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a3b76a2c3aaf4fd6a5a09e26be09d27b0aafc9","tid":2234992,"uid":151926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"護士通常著白色吊帶絲襪"},{"pid":"6c9927908d68da2a71244cb71ab61b080b9044c8","tid":2234992,"uid":220922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"通常癲癲地"},{"pid":"1d512dc62746ee989600eb3a5d6d2c84e8aab91e","tid":2234992,"uid":64469,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定太樣衰，姑娘覺得你督眼督鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25602c313e33d20a5d5249cbcd7791f36e678871","tid":2234992,"uid":136797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"樓主都on9<br />\n阻撚住人做野"},{"pid":"396dc523442dd0f